Dear Mr. Oder,
today I tried to call you on the phone without success.
As a follow up on our letter dated July 15, 2019, ref. WA 54-QB 4301-2019/0005 (please see attachment) I
would like to ask you some additional questions regarding the business relationship between Wirecard and
First Data.

In detail I am interested in the period from January 1, 2017 until today:
Can you please provide a list of First Data's subsidiaries, joint ventures or shareholdings having a business
relationship with Wirecard (respectively Wirecard Bank AG or Wirecard Acquiring & Issuing GmbH). In case
there is more than one company on First Data's side having a business relationship to Wirecard, I would like
to ask you to answer my further questions separately for each of it:
1.  The start of the business relationship.
2. Can you describe the services provided by First Data and Wirecard?
3.  What was the total revenue on both sides generated out of the business relationship in each year?
4. Was there any indicator of money laundering, fraud or other misbehavior on Wirecard group's side?
5. Was the business relationship terminated? If so, when? and by whom? and why?

Thank you very much again for your support!
Mit freundlichen Grüßen / Kind regards

Dear Mr. Oder,
today I tried to call you on the phone without success.
As a follow up on our letter dated July 15, 2019, ref. WA 54-QB 4301-2019/0005 (please see attachment) I
would like to ask you some additional questions regarding the business relationship between Wirecard and
First Data.

In detail I am interested in the period from January 1, 2017 until today:
Can you please provide a list of First Data's subsidiaries, joint ventures or shareholdings having a business
relationship with Wirecard (respectively Wirecard Bank AG or Wirecard Acquiring & Issuing GmbH). In case
there is more than one company on First Data's side having a business relationship to Wirecard, I would like
to ask you to answer my further questions separately for each of it:

1. The start of the business relationship.
2. Can you describe the services provided by First Data and Wirecard?
3. What was the total revenue on both sides generated out of the business relationship in each year?
4. Was there any indicator of money laundering, fraud or other misbehavior on Wirecard group's side?
5. Was the business relationship terminated? If so, when? and by whom? and why?

Thank you very much again for your support!

Mit freundlichen Grüßen / Kind regards

Markus Scherer
